{"tid":545973,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[含圖] 歐洲紅魔主場之旅  撞到伍家謙","createTime":"2018-01-31T05:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T09:44:10.000Z","uid":138214,"like":19,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7614937081f6dc25d9f1ffa1cc7a74cf93435386","tid":545973,"uid":138214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:02:15.000Z","msg":"今次歐遊去咗參觀紅魔主場，不過唔係去皇者曼個Old Toilet，而係揀咗「歐洲紅魔」比利時個國家隊主場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/125914_113e3f39f8dfaf28a651ff476cac3113.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F125914_113e3f39f8dfaf28a651ff476cac3113.JPG&h=bd410c54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飛機過兩個月先有直航，所以今次要喺倫敦轉機，好彩趕得切本身班機，如果唔係都唔知要等幾耐。晨早流流落機就去咗去喺首都布魯塞爾嘅國家隊主場&mdash;博杜安國王體育場 (King Baudouin Stadium)。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/130009_01b912fd54ced2c72a4d6d008a50d163.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F130009_01b912fd54ced2c72a4d6d008a50d163.JPG&h=4c33ffce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一點鐘 肚好L餓,仲有好多圖食完飯返黎POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c1b02f29f5db7435a1204e7a2af7cd55e2b764","tid":545973,"uid":10975,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"Po得果2張係#1, 不如咪撚開"},{"pid":"2776f9c5208244c6f73f0a9872ea63b5dc9c11a9","tid":545973,"uid":138214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c1b02f29f5db7435a1204e7a2af7cd55e2b764","tid":545973,"uid":10975,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"Po得果2張係#1, 不如咪撚開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:16:19.000Z","msg":"呢個球場前身就係各位波台手足都知嘅「希素球場」，本身對呢個球場嘅認識就淨係得「希素球場慘劇」，好在有職員帶住同詳細講解。原來高柏尼、爆炸頭、贊球王、包輸阿姨都係布魯塞爾出身，加埋當地球會安德烈治，睇嚟呢個首都城市嘅球味都真係幾濃。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/131533_c4373abc39fb9b3d367413fdd9b9898a.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F131533_c4373abc39fb9b3d367413fdd9b9898a.JPG&h=da8efa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/131538_7ae649871187257ba7343a19828b8a31.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F131538_7ae649871187257ba7343a19828b8a31.JPG&h=adb0e8b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[img][/img]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/131554_a5445952fcb1a3dcc6e24f6138cb75bd.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F131554_a5445952fcb1a3dcc6e24f6138cb75bd.JPG&h=a9a5e9e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f592c6802f2cb22d7fe7f7652357bb1397de06e","tid":545973,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"邊撚度有伍家謙"},{"pid":"4cf9dc837753feeadadfe22658601f19ccbc85e8","tid":545973,"uid":57036,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"你撞到伍家謙，我撞到摩連奴添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e7f48b0577afc8e483786ec97865354f5a98773","tid":545973,"uid":138214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00c1b02f29f5db7435a1204e7a2af7cd55e2b764","tid":545973,"uid":10975,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"Po得果2張係#1, 不如咪撚開"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:18:18.000Z","msg":"Ching我岩岩買外賣 爬完飯POST淨埋低個啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cc9c5105369a6c4ac3e7cb7c711eb5b2479c66","tid":545973,"uid":138214,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"4cf9dc837753feeadadfe22658601f19ccbc85e8","tid":545973,"uid":57036,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"你撞到伍家謙，我撞到摩連奴添呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"成個tour主要都係睇吓個球場、看台同主客更衣室呢啲基本嘢，同埋了解吓比利時足球歷史，作為朝早一落機嘅節目都幾輕鬆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/133534_19cbb9d623318cca36bd00a4cbe15a22.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F133534_19cbb9d623318cca36bd00a4cbe15a22.JPG&h=ab98c1ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/133536_1dadd1f2933419dd27b0c07aa1811476.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F133536_1dadd1f2933419dd27b0c07aa1811476.JPG&h=1dd8c3e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/133538_aee107db0cab162adf433b31c83ba9fc.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F133538_aee107db0cab162adf433b31c83ba9fc.JPG&h=58a878e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個球場tour唔算太熱門，去到得幾丁友，好彩我一個禮拜前上網填form預約咗，原來個導遊要有人book先會喺度，就咁walk-in係無得入去。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n臨走喺門口見到伍家謙，唔知喺度拍緊乜。佢份人都幾nice，行埋去搵佢影咗張相同吹咗幾句就出返市中心食lunch喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/133717_df9a6ed288c3151da274d6595a2b4c53.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F133717_df9a6ed288c3151da274d6595a2b4c53.JPG&h=a7aa7a32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb27ee3ac5ab2bf79f3aab80ae8f8da98351ef8c","tid":545973,"uid":138083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:08:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"197956768d3e56d5e2c9eceaf40f2d1651e836ee","tid":545973,"uid":144769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:20:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"05830c3564451dfddf36d4c93b978a81c69931f1","tid":545973,"uid":12980,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"你直接貼伍家謙咪得<br />\n其他野冇人想知"},{"pid":"eab30639beaec017940b09b4e3ea35a6f4f57bc6","tid":545973,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05830c3564451dfddf36d4c93b978a81c69931f1","tid":545973,"uid":12980,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"你直接貼伍家謙咪得<br />\n其他野冇人想知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed70ee3e4e97c90a402dd66a8e89aca288707c42","tid":545973,"uid":168506,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"059ee72a51a353b0722c2b861a304a863c028d5b","tid":545973,"uid":57036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eab30639beaec017940b09b4e3ea35a6f4f57bc6","tid":545973,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05830c3564451dfddf36d4c93b978a81c69931f1","tid":545973,"uid":12980,"like":24,"dislike":7,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"你直接貼伍家謙咪得<br />\n其他野冇人想知"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T06:24:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-